README

This is an educational tool that uses a narrative style to reinforce basic unix skills.

To use the enchanted forest tutorial...TBD

Open a unix environment (on mac, open "terminal", on PC use WSL2)

# download the zipped folder
wget https://github.com/IvoryC/enchanted_forest_unix_tutorial/archive/refs/heads/main.zip

# unzip the folder
unzip main.zip

# enter the folder
cd enchanted_forest_unix_tutorial

# see the instructions
cat welcome_beginners.txt

# enter the forest
cd the_enchanted_forest


If you get an error like "wget: command not found" then try this instead:
curl -0 https://github.com/IvoryC/enchanted_forest_unix_tutorial/archive/refs/heads/main.zip

For developers seeking to extend the enchanted forest, see for_developers.

For instructors seeking to use the tool, see for_instructors.

